<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="relieve-vt">relieve <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'liːv/    美 /rɪ'liːv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使减轻；使解除 (痛苦、忧愁等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anxiety may be relieved by talking to a friend. 
和朋友谈谈可以减轻焦虑。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>relieved /rɪ'liːvd/ adj   </p></div>